+# 🚀 Quick Start Guide
+
+Get the eSIM Platform running in **5 minutes**.
+
+## Prerequisites
+
+- Node.js 18+ ([download](https://nodejs.org))
+- Docker Desktop ([download](https://docker.com/products/docker-desktop))
+
+## Step 1: Start Infrastructure (1 min)
+
+```bash
+# Start PostgreSQL and Redis
+docker-compose up -d
+
+# Verify services are running
+docker-compose ps
+```
+
+## Step 2: Backend Setup (2 min)
+
+```bash
+# Navigate to backend
+cd apps/api
+
+# Install dependencies
+npm install
+npm run prisma:generate
+
+# Set up environment
+cp .env.example .env
+# Optional: Edit .env with your credentials
+
+# Generate Prisma client
+npx prisma generate
+
+# Run database migrations
+npx prisma migrate dev
+
+# Seed demo data
+npx prisma db seed
+
+# Start backend
+npm run dev
+```
+
+✅ Backend running at http://localhost:3001
+
+## Step 3: Frontend Setup (2 min)
+
+Open a **new terminal** window:
+
+```bash
+# Navigate to frontend
+cd apps/web
+
+# Install dependencies
+npm install
+npm run prisma:generate
+
+# Set up environment
+cp .env.local.example .env.local
+
+# Start frontend
+npm run dev
+```
+
+✅ Frontend running at http://localhost:3000
+
+## Step 4: Access Application
+
+Open your browser to:
+
+**http://localhost:3000**
+
+### Demo Login
+
+- **Email**: `admin@example.com`
+- **Password**: `SecurePassword123!` (or your ADMIN_PASSWORD from .env)
+
+## 🎉 You're Ready!
+
+### What to Try
+
+1. **Dashboard** - View real-time metrics
+2. **Lines** - Manage eSIM lines
+3. **Provision** - Create new eSIM line
+4. **Search** - Filter and search lines
+5. **Actions** - Suspend/Resume/Terminate
+
+## Troubleshooting
+
+### Port Already in Use
+
+```bash
+# Check what's using port 3000 or 3001
+lsof -i :3000
+lsof -i :3001
+
+# Kill the process
+kill -9 <PID>
+```
+
+### Database Connection Failed
+
+```bash
+# Ensure Docker is running
+docker-compose ps
+
+# Restart services
+docker-compose down
+docker-compose up -d
+```
+
+### Frontend Can't Reach Backend
+
+1. Check backend is running: http://localhost:3001/health
+2. Verify NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL in `apps/web/.env.local`
+3. Restart frontend: `npm run dev`
+
+## Development Workflow
+
+### Run Both Apps Together
+
+From root directory:
+
+```bash
+npm run dev
+```
+
+### View Database
+
+```bash
+# Open Prisma Studio
+npm run db:studio
+```
+
+### Reset Database
+
+```bash
+cd apps/api
+npx prisma migrate reset
+npx prisma db seed
+```
+
+## Next Steps
+
+- Read `README.md` for complete documentation
+- Check `DEPLOYMENT.md` for production deployment
+- Explore API at http://localhost:3001/health
+
+## Need Help?
+
+- Check logs: `docker-compose logs -f`
+- View backend logs in terminal
+- Inspect network tab in browser DevTools
+
+---
+
+Happy coding! 🎨
