+# 🚀 eSIM Platform - Full-Stack Application
+
+Complete, production-ready eSIM management platform with beautiful Next.js frontend and Express.js backend.
+
+## ✨ What's Built
+
+### Frontend (Next.js 14)
+- **Beautiful, Modern UI** - Distinctive design with gradients, glass morphism, and a hardened app shell
+- **Dashboard** - Real-time metrics, line management, analytics
+- **Lines Management** - Live inventory search, filtering, export, and status controls
+- **Login/Auth** - Tenant-aware authentication flow with role-aware actions
+- **Animations** - Smooth transitions and lightweight operator-friendly interactions
+- **Responsive** - Mobile-first, works on all devices
+
+### Backend (Express.js + Prisma)
+- **RESTful API** - Complete endpoints for all features
+- **JWT Authentication** - Secure access + refresh tokens
+- **PostgreSQL Database** - 14 tables with Prisma ORM
+- **Async Provisioning** - Queue-ready job layer with simulated provisioning flow
+- **Security** - Helmet, CORS, rate limiting, RBAC, readiness checks, signed webhook verification
+- **Telnyx Integration** - Real eSIM provisioning
+
+## 🎯 Quick Start (5 Minutes)
+
+### Prerequisites
+```bash
+Node.js 18+
+Docker & Docker Compose
+```
+
+### 1. Start Infrastructure
+```bash
+docker-compose up -d
+```
+
+This starts:
+- PostgreSQL (port 5432)
+- Redis (port 6379)
+
+### 2. Set Up Backend
+```bash
+cd apps/api
+npm install
+cp .env.example .env
+# Edit .env with your credentials
+npx prisma generate
+npx prisma migrate dev
+npx prisma db seed
+npm run dev
+```
+
+Backend runs on http://localhost:3001
+
+### 3. Start Frontend
+```bash
+cd apps/web
+npm install
+npm run dev
+```
+
+Frontend runs on http://localhost:3000
+
+### 4. Open Application
+Visit http://localhost:3000
+
+**Demo Login:**
+- Email: `admin@example.com`
+- Password: (set in your .env as ADMIN_PASSWORD)
+
+## 📂 Project Structure
+
+```
+esim-fullstack/
+├── apps/
+│   ├── api/              # Backend Express.js API
+│   │   ├── src/
+│   │   │   ├── routes/   # API routes
+│   │   │   ├── middleware/
+│   │   │   ├── services/ # Business logic
+│   │   │   ├── lib/      # Utilities
+│   │   │   └── jobs/     # Background jobs
+│   │   ├── prisma/       # Database schema
+│   │   └── package.json
+│   │
+│   └── web/              # Frontend Next.js 14
+│       ├── src/
+│       │   ├── app/      # Pages (App Router)
+│       │   │   ├── page.tsx           # Dashboard
+│       │   │   ├── login/page.tsx     # Login
+│       │   │   └── lines/page.tsx     # Lines Management
+│       │   ├── components/
+│       │   ├── lib/      # API client, utils
+│       │   └── styles/   # Global CSS
+│       └── package.json
+│
+├── docker-compose.yml    # Local development
+└── package.json          # Monorepo root
+
+## 🎨 Frontend Features
+
+### Design System
+- **Colors**: Navy blue (primary) + Orange (accent)
+- **Typography**: modern sans + monospace operator-friendly data styling
+- **Components**: Glass cards, gradient buttons, animated badges
+- **Animations**: Staggered reveals, smooth transitions
+
+### Pages
+
+**Dashboard (`/`)**
+- Real-time metrics (total lines, active, provisioning, usage)
+- Recent lines table with actions
+- Quick action cards
+- Responsive grid layout
+
+**Lines Management (`/lines`)**
+- Searchable, filterable table
+- Line status management (suspend, resume, terminate)
+- Bulk operations
+- Pagination
+- Export to CSV
+
+**Login (`/login`)**
+- Split-screen design
+- JWT authentication
+- Remember me functionality
+- Password reset flow
+- Mobile responsive
+
+### Components
+- MetricCard - Animated stat cards
+- StatusBadge - Color-coded status indicators
+- Table - Sortable, filterable data tables
+- Navigation - Sticky header with branding
+- Buttons - Multiple variants (primary, secondary, accent)
+
+## 🔧 Backend Features
+
+### API Endpoints
+
+**Authentication**
+- `POST /api/auth/login` - User login
+- `POST /api/auth/register` - Create account
+- `POST /api/auth/refresh` - Refresh token
+- `POST /api/auth/logout` - Logout
+
+**Lines Management**
+- `GET /api/lines` - List lines (paginated)
+- `POST /api/lines` - Provision new line
+- `GET /api/lines/:id` - Get line details
+- `DELETE /api/lines/:id` - Terminate line
+- `POST /api/lines/:id/suspend` - Suspend line
+- `POST /api/lines/:id/resume` - Resume line
+
+**Dashboard**
+- `GET /api/dashboard/metrics` - Platform metrics (cached)
+
+**Audit**
+- `GET /api/audit` - Audit logs (paginated + filterable by action/actor)
+
+**Webhooks**
+- `POST /api/webhooks/telnyx` - Telnyx events with HMAC verification support
+
+### Database Schema (14 Tables)
+
+- `tenants` - Multi-tenant organizations
+- `users` - User accounts with roles
+- `lines` - eSIM lines (MSISDN, ICCID, status)
+- `esim_profiles` - Activation codes, QR data
+- `provision_jobs` - Background job tracking
+- `plans` - Data plans
+- `bundles` - Plan + addon combinations
+- `addons` - Extra features
+- `line_bundles` - Active line subscriptions
+- `line_addons` - Active line features
+- `usage_records` - Data consumption logs
+- `webhooks` - Telnyx callbacks
+- `audit_logs` - Complete activity trail
+- `api_keys` - Programmatic access
+
+### Security
+
+- **JWT Tokens**: Access (15min) + Refresh (7 days)
+- **RBAC**: ADMIN/USER mutation access with VIEWER read-only enforcement
+- **Password Hashing**: bcrypt (10 rounds)
+- **Rate Limiting**: 100 req/15min (general), 5 req/15min (auth)
+- **CORS**: Strict origin control
+- **Helmet**: Security headers (CSP, HSTS, XSS)
+- **Readiness Checks**: `/health` and `/health/ready`
+- **Signed Webhooks**: Constant-time HMAC verification with timestamp tolerance
+- **Request Tracing**: UUID per request
+
+### Performance
+
+- **Cursor Pagination**: Scalable for 1000+ records
+- **Redis Caching**: Dashboard metrics (60s TTL)
+- **Database Indexes**: tenantId, status, createdAt
+- **Connection Pooling**: Prisma defaults
+- **Background Jobs**: BullMQ + Redis
+- **Retry Logic**: Exponential backoff (3 attempts)
+
+## 🌐 Environment Variables
+
+### Backend (.env)
+```env
+# Database
+DATABASE_URL=postgresql://esim_user:esim_password_dev@localhost:5432/esim_platform
+
+# JWT Secrets
+JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_here
+REFRESH_TOKEN_SECRET=your_refresh_secret_here
+
+# Admin
+ADMIN_PASSWORD=SecurePassword123!
+
+# Telnyx
+TELNYX_API_KEY=KEY***
+TELNYX_CONNECTION_ID=123456
+TELNYX_MESSAGING_PROFILE_ID=123456
+TELNYX_WEBHOOK_SECRET=webhook_secret
+
+# Application
+FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
+CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000
+
+# Redis
+REDIS_HOST=localhost
+REDIS_PORT=6379
+REDIS_PASSWORD=redis_password_dev
+
+# Server
+NODE_ENV=development
+PORT=3001
+```
+
+### Frontend (.env.local)
+```env
+NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
+```
+
+## 🧪 Development
+
+### Run Both Apps
+```bash
+npm run dev
+```
+
+### Run Individually
+```bash
+# Backend only
+npm run dev:api
+
+# Frontend only
+npm run dev:web
+```
+
+### Database Management
+```bash
+# Create migration
+cd apps/api && npx prisma migrate dev --name add_feature
+
+# Open Prisma Studio
+npm run db:studio
+
+# Seed database
+npm run db:seed
+```
+
+### Docker Commands
+```bash
+# Start services
+docker-compose up -d
+
+# View logs
+docker-compose logs -f
+
+# Stop services
+docker-compose down
+
+# Reset everything
+docker-compose down -v
+```
+
+## 📦 Production Deployment
+
+### Option 1: Docker
+```bash
+docker-compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d
+```
+
+### Option 2: Render + Vercel
+See `DEPLOYMENT.md` for complete guide.
+
+**Backend (Render):**
+1. Create PostgreSQL database
+2. Deploy via Blueprint (render.yaml)
+3. Set environment variables
+4. Run migrations
+
+**Frontend (Vercel):**
+1. Connect GitHub repo
+2. Set root: `apps/web`
+3. Add environment variable: `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`
+4. Deploy
+
