+- **Database**: PostgreSQL
+- **ORM**: Prisma
+- **Cache/Queue**: Redis + BullMQ
+- **Auth**: JWT + bcrypt
+- **Validation**: Zod
+- **Logging**: Winston
+- **Security**: Helmet, CORS, Rate Limit
+
+### Infrastructure
+- **Containerization**: Docker
+- **Database**: PostgreSQL 15
+- **Cache**: Redis 7
+- **Process Manager**: PM2 (production)
